    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375610/extras/db895cf3923a43e15a3566142ffeb1e0.poster.avif?t=1690435535\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375610/extras/db895cf3923a43e15a3566142ffeb1e0.webm?t=1690435535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375610/extras/db895cf3923a43e15a3566142ffeb1e0.mp4?t=1690435535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Breach In Space</strong> is a 2D shooting game with challenging combat and very hard platforming. Find a way back to home galaxy through 4 different planets.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375610/extras/47a4b173eaf2affa19eec7a04e15eff1.poster.avif?t=1690435535\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375610/extras/47a4b173eaf2affa19eec7a04e15eff1.webm?t=1690435535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375610/extras/47a4b173eaf2affa19eec7a04e15eff1.mp4?t=1690435535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Destroy monsters with 4 different weapons and 3 different utilities.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Upgrade your weapons, character and utilities at the space station.<br></li><li>Travel through 4 unique planets to find a way back home.<br></li><li>Each planet contains completely different enemies and an epic boss.<br></li><li>A classic side-scrolling action with tight 2D controls and very hard platforming.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WARNING!</h2><strong>This game is very hard and might cause frustration or even rage.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375610/extras/dbea6c38877715e03964d7217499baf3.poster.avif?t=1690435535\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375610/extras/dbea6c38877715e03964d7217499baf3.webm?t=1690435535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375610/extras/dbea6c38877715e03964d7217499baf3.mp4?t=1690435535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
